{"body": "Hi Jos\u00e9,\r\n\r\nActually-- I tried for quite a while trying to see if there was a way to temporarily disable callbacks this with the current API, and there isn't...\r\n\r\n    class Foo < ActiveRecord::Base\r\n      before_save do\r\n        puts \"callback\"\r\n      end\r\n    end\r\n\r\n> Foo.last.save\r\ncallback\r\n=> true\r\n\r\n> Foo.last.save(:callbacks => false)\r\ncallback\r\n=> true\r\n\r\n...\r\n\r\n-patrick", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3816376", "created_at": "2012-02-05T08:48:05Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/4884#issuecomment-3816376", "updated_at": "2012-02-05T08:48:27Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 4884, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/patrick99e99", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/648553f5c693d93c9ea2e042857ad22c?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F25b6a534a8c88b8e73fe7b865fd36bde.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/received_events", "gravatar_id": "648553f5c693d93c9ea2e042857ad22c", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "patrick99e99", "type": "User", "id": 28946, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/patrick99e99/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52381ffebd3543c15100e86f"}, "id": 3816376, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/4884"}
